highlights.text: “DIA DELÍCIA” by Nakama and ΣP is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Sweden, up 20 spots at #80.
“The Glen - Levi Heron Edit” by Levi Heron has been on Viral Songs Sweden the longest, at 84 days straight.
KPop Demon Hunters Cast has the most spots on Viral Songs Sweden. “Golden” is the highest at #7.
“ACELERADA” by sma$her and MXZI is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Sweden at #47.
